lonely and leaves us

00:04:29.290 --> 00:04:33.150 align:middle line:84%
with many basic human
needs that go unmet.

00:04:33.150 --> 00:04:35.670 align:middle line:84%
And if you have
money, you might try

00:04:35.670 --> 00:04:39.780 align:middle line:84%
to fill this hunger
through purchasing,

00:04:39.780 --> 00:04:42.330 align:middle line:84%
through buying things, or
through accumulating money

00:04:42.330 --> 00:04:43.930 align:middle line:90%
itself.

00:04:43.930 --> 00:04:46.810 align:middle line:84%
And of course, now we're
nearing the end of growth.

00:04:46.810 --> 00:04:50.910 align:middle line:84%
The planet can't sustain
much more growth.

00:04:50.910 --> 00:04:53.780 align:middle line:84%
And that's why the crisis that
we have today won't go away.

